    <scopecontent id="aspace_e5d9c5198a1d5e27236268911bf72a25">
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>This collection includes two (2) LPs with a recording of the performance at Washington National Cathedral's Gloria in Excelsis Tower dedication, as well as a book of the dedication ceremony, which includes sheet music.</p>
    </scopecontent>
